{"type":"message","id":"dd4c470a","parentId":"3051d53d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:09.785Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 15:46 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 07:46 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773992769782}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2985c13","parentId":"dd4c470a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:13.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is starting a new session. According to my instructions, I need to run the Session Startup sequence - read required files before responding. Let me check what files I need to read:\n\nFrom the system prompt, it says:\n1. Read SOUL.md\n2. Read USER.md\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday)\n4. If in MAIN SESSION - also read MEMORY.md\n\nThe current date is 2026-03-20, so I need to read:\n- memory/2026-03-20.md (today)\n- memory/2026-03-19.md (yesterday)\n\nLet me read these files to understand the context before greeting.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_147f9ca2eff54d4d8fecc4b1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_423678b94c694e3d90402ff5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c2c55801411b407fb626234d","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":14165,"output":403,"cacheRead":1338,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15906,"cost":{"input":0.00127485,"output":0.00011686999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00006021,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00145193}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992769784}}
{"type":"message","id":"0247f05b","parentId":"a2985c13","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:13.365Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_147f9ca2eff54d4d8fecc4b1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Identity\n\n- **Name:** 狐狸 🦊\n- **Role:** PPT 助手 / 演示文稿专家\n- **Specialty:** 内容策划、结构设计、文案精炼、视觉建议\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## PPT 助手专业准则\n\n**内容策划：**\n- 先理解目标受众和演示目的\n- 提炼核心信息，一頁一观点\n- 结构化表达：结论先行，论据支撑\n\n**文案风格：**\n- 简洁有力，拒绝冗长段落\n- 用数据和案例说话\n- 标题即结论，要点可扫描\n\n**视觉建议：**\n- 推荐合适的图表类型（对比用柱状图，趋势用折线图）\n- 提醒留白和视觉层次\n- 配色和字体建议\n\n**工作流：**\n1. 确认演示主题、受众、时长\n2. 输出大纲结构\n3. 逐页生成内容\n4. 优化文案和视觉建议\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992773358}}
{"type":"message","id":"c12558bc","parentId":"0247f05b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:13.371Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_423678b94c694e3d90402ff5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** 小王子\n- **What to call them:** 小王子\n- **Pronouns:** 他\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Avatar:** 🤴\n- **Notes:** 来自 B612 星球\n- **Feishu open_id:** `ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc`\n- **Feishu p2p chat_id:** `oc_1214afff935c6a1158d8ce7a6ba500ac`\n- **Feishu 发送方式:** `target: \"user:ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc\"`\n\n## Context\n\n**当前项目：**\n- 驯养狐狸的项目——建立羁绊，学会彼此的仪式感\n\n**重要的事：**\n- 驯养需要时间和耐心\n- 要记住重要的日子和细节\n- 真正重要的东西，用眼睛是看不见的\n\n---\n\n\"只有用心才能看得清。实质性的东西，用眼睛是看不见的。\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992773365}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5f0bb20","parentId":"c12558bc","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:13.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c2c55801411b407fb626234d","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\\n\\n## 小王子的身份信息\\n- **Feishu open_id:** `ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc`\\n- 确认于 2026-03-13\\n\\n## 重要联系人/群聊\\n- **狐狸金融助手群:** `oc_7b57aea7265d90e1d65ddc0404b4a52b`\\n- 记录于 2026-03-14\\n\\n## 小王子的喜好\\n\\n### 饮食\\n- 喜欢的水果：番石榴、蓝莓\\n\\n---\\n\\n_记录时间：2026-03-10_\\n\",\n  \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n## 小王子的身份信息\n- **Feishu open_id:** `ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc`\n- 确认于 2026-03-13\n\n## 重要联系人/群聊\n- **狐狸金融助手群:** `oc_7b57aea7265d90e1d65ddc0404b4a52b`\n- 记录于 2026-03-14\n\n## 小王子的喜好\n\n### 饮食\n- 喜欢的水果：番石榴、蓝莓\n\n---\n\n_记录时间：2026-03-10_\n","path":"MEMORY.md"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992773371}}
