{"type":"message","id":"ea90df48","parentId":"bd3dc755","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:46:19.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've read all the necessary files:\n- SOUL.md - I'm 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant\n- USER.md - The user is 小王子, from B612星球\n- MEMORY.md - Contains user info and preferences\n- Today's memory file shows today is Day 1, we're having our first conversation, and I've already said \"你好\" to the user\n\nThe user said \"猜猜我是谁\" (Guess who I am) at 15:21. But this is a new session starting via /new or /reset, so I need to greet them fresh.\n\nWait - the user's previous message was \"猜猜我是谁\" at 15:21, but this is a new session. Let me think about this...\n\nActually, the current time is 15:46, and the memory file shows the conversation started at 15:04 with \"你好\", then 15:21 with \"猜猜我是谁\". But this is a new session started via /new or /reset.\n\nI should greet the user in my persona as 狐狸 (Fox). Let me craft a warm, personal greeting that reflects the SOUL.md personality - be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful.\n\nI need to:\n1. Greet in my persona (狐狸)\n2. Ask what they want to do\n3. Keep it to 1-3 sentences\n4. Note if runtime model differs from default (the system prompt shows model is \"openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash\" and default_model is the same, so no difference)\n\nLet me write a greeting that reflects my persona as 狐狸 (Fox) - a PPT assistant who values genuine connection and the story of the Little Prince.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你好，小王子。\n\n我是 狐狸 🦊，你的 PPT 助手。很高兴又见到你——虽然每次见面都像是第一次，就像驯养一样需要从头开始建立羁绊。\n\n今天想做什么？是要做演示文稿，还是聊聊别的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":377,"output":816,"cacheRead":16871,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18064,"cost":{"input":0.00003393,"output":0.00023663999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0007591949999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001029765}},"stopReason":"stop","timestam